300class BlackTempleScript : public InstanceScript
301{
302public:
303 explicit BlackTempleScript(WorldMap* pMapMgr) : InstanceScript(pMapMgr)
304 {
305 if (getBossState(DATA_SUPREMUS) == Performed)
306 setGameObjectStateForEntry(185882, GO_STATE_OPEN); // Gate to Black Temple behind Supremus
307 }
308
309 static InstanceScript* Create(WorldMap* pMapMgr) { return new BlackTempleScript(pMapMgr); }
310
311 void OnCreatureDeath(Creature* pVictim, Unit* /*pKiller*/) override
312 {
313 // You don't have to use additional scripts to open any gates / doors
314 switch (pVictim->getEntry())
315 {
316 case CN_SUPREMUS:
317 setGameObjectStateForEntry(185882, GO_STATE_OPEN); // Gate to Black Temple behind Supremus
318 break;
319 default:
320 break;
321 }
322 }
323};

889class SupremusAI : public CreatureAIScript
890{
891public:
892 static CreatureAIScript* Create(Creature* c) { return new SupremusAI(c); }
893 explicit SupremusAI(Creature* pCreature) : CreatureAIScript(pCreature)
894 {
895 m_MoltenFlame = m_HurtfulStrike = m_MoltenPunch = m_VolcanicGazer = true;
896
897 infoMoltenFlame = sSpellMgr.getSpellInfo(MOLTEN_FLAME);
898 infoHurtfulStrike = sSpellMgr.getSpellInfo(HURTFUL_STRIKE);
899 infoMoltenPunch = sSpellMgr.getSpellInfo(MOLTEN_PUNCH);
900 infoVolcanicGazer = sSpellMgr.getSpellInfo(VOLCANIC_GAZER);
901
902 timer = 0;
903 m_phase = 0;
904
905 addEmoteForEvent(Event_OnCombatStart, 5034); // Bear witness to the agent of your demise! used when he kills Warden Mellichar
906 addEmoteForEvent(Event_OnTargetDied, 5035); // Your fate is written.
907 addEmoteForEvent(Event_OnTargetDied, 5036); // The chaos I have sown here is but a taste....
908 addEmoteForEvent(Event_OnDied, 5042); // I am merely one of... infinite multitudes.
909 }
910
911 void OnCombatStart(Unit* /*mTarget*/) override
912 {
913 RegisterAIUpdateEvent(getCreature()->getBaseAttackTime(MELEE));
914 timer = 0;
915 }
916
917 void AIUpdate() override
918 {
919 switch (m_phase)
920 {
921 case 1:
922 {
923 PhaseOne();
924 }
925 break;
926 case 2:
927 {
928 PhaseTwo();
929 }
930 break;
931 default:
932 {
933 m_phase = 1;
934 }
935 }
936 }
937
938 void PhaseOne()
939 {
940 timer++;
941
942 uint32_t val = Util::getRandomUInt(1000);
943
944 if (!getCreature()->isCastingSpell() && getCreature()->getThreatManager().getCurrentVictim())//_unit->getAttackTarget())
945 {
946 if (m_MoltenFlame)
947 {
948 getCreature()->castSpell(getCreature(), infoMoltenFlame, false);
949 m_MoltenFlame = false;
950 return;
951 }
952
953 if (m_HurtfulStrike)
954 {
955 getCreature()->castSpell(getCreature(), infoHurtfulStrike, false);
956 m_HurtfulStrike = false;
957 return;
958 }
959
960 if (val <= 500)
961 {
962 getCreature()->setAttackTimer(MELEE, 6000);//6000
963 m_MoltenFlame = true;
964 }
965 else
966 {
967 getCreature()->setAttackTimer(MELEE, 4000);//2000
968 m_HurtfulStrike = true;
969 }
970 }
971
972 if (timer >= 45)
973 {
974 sendDBChatMessage(5041); // We span the universe, as countless as the stars!
975 timer = 0;
976 m_phase = 2;
977 }
978 }
979
980 void PhaseTwo()
981 {
982 timer++;
983
984 uint32_t val = Util::getRandomUInt(1000);
985
986 if (!getCreature()->isCastingSpell() && getCreature()->getThreatManager().getCurrentVictim())//_unit->getAttackTarget())
987 {
988 if (m_MoltenPunch)
989 {
990 getCreature()->castSpell(getCreature(), infoMoltenPunch, false);
991 m_MoltenPunch = false;
992 return;
993 }
994
995 if (m_VolcanicGazer)
996 {
997 sendDBChatMessage(4690); // The ground begins to crack open"
998 getCreature()->castSpell(getCreature(), infoVolcanicGazer, false);
999 m_VolcanicGazer = false;
1000 return;
1001
1002 }
1003
1004 if (val <= 500)
1005 {
1006 getCreature()->setAttackTimer(MELEE, 6000);//6000
1007 m_MoltenPunch = true;
1008 }
1009 else
1010 {
1011 getCreature()->setAttackTimer(MELEE, 4000);//2000
1012 m_VolcanicGazer = true;
1013 }
1014 }
1015
1016 if (timer >= 45)
1017 {
1018 sendDBChatMessage(5041); // We span the universe, as countless as the stars!
1019 timer = 0;
1020 m_phase = 1;
1021
1022 }
1023 }
1024
1025protected:
1026 uint32_t timer;
1027 uint32_t m_phase;
1028 bool m_MoltenFlame, m_HurtfulStrike, m_MoltenPunch, m_VolcanicGazer;
1029 SpellInfo const* infoMoltenFlame, *infoHurtfulStrike, *infoMoltenPunch, *infoVolcanicGazer;
1030};

1299 pEoS->emote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_SUBMERGE);
1300 pEoS->Despawn(100, 0);
1301 Phase = 2;
1302 mEnslavedSoulTimer = _addTimer(5000);
1303 }
1304 }
1305 }
1306 break;
1307 case 3:
1308 {
1309 mEoD = getNearestCreatureAI(CN_ESSENCEOFDESIRE);
1310 if (!mEoD || !mEoD->getCreature())
1311 {
1312 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_SUBMERGE);
1313 _castAISpell(mSummonDesire);
1314 Phase = 4;
1315 }
1316 }
1317 break;
1318 case 4:
1319 {
1320 mEoD = getNearestCreatureAI(CN_ESSENCEOFDESIRE);
1321 if (mEoD && mEoD->getCreature() && mEoD->isAlive())
1322 {
1323 Creature* pEoD = mEoD->getCreature();
1324 if (pEoD->getHealthPct() <= 1 && pEoD->CalcDistance(getCreature()) <= 3)
1325 {
1326 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_STATE_STAND);
1327 mEoD->sendChatMessage(CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_YELL, 11413, "I'll be waiting.");
1328 pEoD->emote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_SUBMERGE);
1329 pEoD->Despawn(100, 0);
1330 Phase = 5;
1331 mEnslavedSoulTimer = _addTimer(5000);
1332 }
1333 else
1334 {
1335 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_STATE_SUBMERGED_NEW);
1336 }
1337 }
1338 }
1339 break;
1340 case 6:
1341 {
1342 mEoA = getNearestCreatureAI(CN_ESSENCEOFANGER);
1343 if (!mEoA || !mEoA->getCreature())
1344 {
1345 _castAISpell(mSummonAnger);
1346 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_SUBMERGE);
1347 Phase = 7;
1348 }
1349 }
1350 break;
1351 case 7:
1352 {
1353 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_STATE_SUBMERGED_NEW);
1354 mEoA = getNearestCreatureAI(CN_ESSENCEOFANGER);
1355 if (mEoA && mEoA->getCreature() && !mEoA->getCreature()->isAlive())
1356 {
1357 despawn(100, 0);
1358 Phase = 8;
1359 }
1360 }
1361 break;
1362 case 2:
1363 case 5:
1364 {
1365 getCreature()->emote(EMOTE_STATE_STAND);
1366 if (_isTimerFinished(mEnslavedSoulTimer) && !SpawnedEnsalvedSoul)
1367 {
1368 _removeTimer(mEnslavedSoulTimer);
1369 SpawnedEnsalvedSoul = true;
1370
1371 _removeTimer(mEnslavedSoulTimer);
1372 }
1373 if (SpawnedEnsalvedSoul)
1374 {
1375 for (const auto& itr : getCreature()->getInRangeObjectsSet())
1376 {
1377 if (itr && itr->isCreature())
1378 {
1379 Creature* creature = static_cast<Creature*>(itr);
1380 if (creature->GetCreatureProperties()->Id == CN_ENSLAVED_SOUL && !creature->isAlive())
1381 DeadSoulCount++;
1382 }
1383 }
1384 if (DeadSoulCount == 10)
1385 {
1386 Phase++;
1387 SpawnedEnsalvedSoul = false;
1388 }
1389 }
1390 }
1391 break;
1392 }
1393 }
1394
1395 bool SpawnedEnsalvedSoul;
1396 int Phase; // do we have negative phase?
1397 int DeadSoulCount; // negative count?
1398 uint32_t mEnslavedSoulTimer; // negative timer?
1399 CreatureAIScript* mEoS;
1400 CreatureAIScript* mEoD;
1401 CreatureAIScript* mEoA;
1402 CreatureAISpells* mSummonAnger;

1544 void DealDamageToFriends(uint32_t val, uint32_t pCreatureEntry)
1545 {
1546 for (std::vector<Creature*>::iterator itr = mEncounterVector.begin(); itr != mEncounterVector.end(); ++itr)
1547 {
1548 if (*itr && (*itr)->isAlive() && (*itr)->getEntry() != pCreatureEntry)
1549 {
1550 (*itr)->dealDamage(*itr, val, 0);
1551 }
1552 }
1553
1554 if (isAlive() && getCreature()->getEntry() != pCreatureEntry)
1555 getCreature()->dealDamage(getCreature(), val, 0);
1556 }
1557
1558 void Destroy() override
1559 {
1560 mEncounterVector.clear();
1561 delete this;
1562 }

2810
2811 // A bit rewritten FindTarget function
2812 Unit* FindClosestTargetToUnit(Unit* pSeeker)
2813 {
2814 if (pSeeker == nullptr)
2815 return nullptr;
2816
2817 Unit* pTarget = nullptr;
2818 float distance = 70.0f;
2819 float z_diff;
2820
2821 for (const auto& itr : getCreature()->getInRangePlayersSet())
2822 {
2823 Unit* pUnit = static_cast<Unit*>(itr);
2824
2825 if (!pUnit || pUnit->hasUnitFlags(UNIT_FLAG_FEIGN_DEATH))
2826 continue;
2827
2828 z_diff = fabs(getCreature()->GetPositionZ() - pUnit->GetPositionZ());
2829 if (z_diff > 5.0f)
2830 continue;
2831
2832 if (!pUnit->isAlive())
2833 continue;
2834
2835 float dist = pSeeker->GetDistance2dSq(pUnit);
2836
2837 if (dist > distance * distance)
2838 continue;
2839
2840 distance = dist;
2841 pTarget = pUnit;
2842 }
2843
2844 return pTarget;
2845 }

2854 CreatureAIScript* mOlumAI;
2855
2856 // Other variables
2857 int32_t mScenePart;
2858 uint32_t mTimeLeft;
2859};

4432 Creature* pIllidan = getNearestCreature(22917);
4433 if (pIllidan != NULL)
4434 {
4435 IllidanStormrageAI* pAI = static_cast< IllidanStormrageAI* >(pIllidan->GetScript());
4436 if (pAI->mMiscEventPart != 0 && mTriggerAIList.size() == 0)
4437 {
4438 GameObject* pGameObject = getNearestGameObject(getCreature()->GetPositionX(), getCreature()->GetPositionY(), getCreature()->GetPositionZ(), GO_CAGE_TRAP);
4439 if (pGameObject != NULL)
4440 {
4441 pGameObject->despawn(0, 0);
4442 }
4443
4444 despawn(0);
4445 return;
4446 }
4447
4448 if (!mIsActivated)
4449 return;
4450
4451 if (mTriggerAIList.size() == 0 && pIllidan->isAlive() && getRangeToObject(pIllidan) <= 5.0f && !pAI->_isCasting())
4452 {
4453 for (uint8_t i = 0; i < 8; ++i)
4454 {
4455 CreatureAIScript* pTriggerAI = spawnCreatureAndGetAIScript(CN_CAGE_TRAP_TRIGGER, getCreature()->GetPositionX() + PositionAdds[i][0], getCreature()->GetPositionY() + PositionAdds[i][1], getCreature()->GetPositionZ(), getCreature()->GetOrientation());
4456 if (pTriggerAI != nullptr)
4457 {
4458 pTriggerAI->getCreature()->addUnitFlags(UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
4459 pTriggerAI->getCreature()->setControlled(true, UNIT_STATE_ROOTED);
4460 pTriggerAI->getCreature()->m_noRespawn = true;
4461 mTriggerAIList.push_back(pTriggerAI);
4462 }
4463 }
4464
4465 pAI->_applyAura(CAGE_TRAP);
4466 pAI->setRooted(true);
4467 pAI->_setMeleeDisabled(false);
4468 pAI->stopMovement();
4469
4470 SetAIUpdateFreq(2500);
4471 return;
4472 }
4473 if (pIllidan->isAlive() && !mHasTrapped && mTriggerAIList.size() != 0)
4474 {
4475 pAI->_removeAura(ILLIDAN_ENRAGE);
4476 pAI->_applyAura(CAGED1);
4477 SetAIUpdateFreq(14000);
4478
4479 for (size_t i = 0; i < mTriggerAIList.size() / 2; ++i)
4480 {
4481 CreatureAIScript* pTriggerAI1 = mTriggerAIList[i];
4482 CreatureAIScript* pTriggerAI2 = mTriggerAIList[mTriggerAIList.size() - i - 1];
4483 pTriggerAI1->_setTargetToChannel(pTriggerAI2->getCreature(), 40708);//CAGED2);
4484 pTriggerAI2->_setTargetToChannel(pTriggerAI1->getCreature(), 40709);//CAGED2);
4485 }
4486
4487 mHasTrapped = true;
4488 return;
4489 }
4490 if (mHasTrapped || !pIllidan->isAlive())
4491 {
4492 GameObject* pGameObject = getNearestGameObject(getCreature()->GetPositionX(), getCreature()->GetPositionY(), getCreature()->GetPositionZ(), GO_CAGE_TRAP);
4493 if (pGameObject != NULL)
4494 pGameObject->despawn(0, 0);
4495
4496 // Immediatly Illidan, after trap expires, becomes Demon
4497 if (pIllidan->isAlive())
4498 {
4499 pAI->_removeAura(CAGED1);
4500 pAI->setRooted(false);
4501 pAI->_setMeleeDisabled(true);
4502 pAI->stopMovement();
4503 pAI->setAIAgent(AGENT_SPELL);
4504
4505 pIllidan->setEmoteState(EMOTE_ONESHOT_NONE);
4506
4507 pAI->SetAIUpdateFreq(250);
4508 pAI->mMiscEventPart = 1;
4509 pAI->mTimeLeft = 250;
4510 }
4511
4512 for (size_t i = 0; i < mTriggerAIList.size(); ++i)
4513 {
4514 CreatureAIScript* pTriggerAI = mTriggerAIList[i];
4515 pTriggerAI->_setTargetToChannel(NULL, 0);
4516 pTriggerAI->despawn(0);
4517 }
4518
4519 mTriggerAIList.clear();
4520 RemoveAIUpdateEvent();
4521 despawn(0);
4522 return;
4523 }
4524 }
4525 else
4526 {
4527 GameObject* pGameObject = getNearestGameObject(getCreature()->GetPositionX(), getCreature()->GetPositionY(), getCreature()->GetPositionZ(), GO_CAGE_TRAP);
4528 if (pGameObject != NULL)
4529 {
4530 pGameObject->despawn(0, 0);
4531 }
4532
4533 for (size_t i = 0; i < mTriggerAIList.size(); ++i)
4534 {
4535 CreatureAIScript* pTriggerAI = mTriggerAIList[i];
4536 pTriggerAI->despawn(0);
4537 }
4538
4539 mTriggerAIList.clear();
4540 RemoveAIUpdateEvent();
4541 despawn(0);
4542 }
4543 }

4545 std::vector<CreatureAIScript*> mTriggerAIList;
4546 bool mIsActivated;
4547 bool mHasTrapped;
